OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782676071
OL,3,CMan who damaged phone and media masts
OL,4,Cfound not criminally responsible
OL,6,FA man who damaged phone and media
OL,7,Fmasts across Jersey was having a
OL,8,Fpsychotic episode at the time, the
OL,9,Fisland's Magistrate's Court has been
OL,10,Ftold.
OL,12,FMariusz Szymanski, 45, was found not
OL,13,Fto be criminally responsible because
OL,14,Fof the condition that he was in, as a
OL,15,Fspecial verdict was recorded following
OL,16,Fexpert evidence.
OL,18,FThe court heard that he was seeing the
OL,19,Fdevil, hoarding food, covering mirrors
OL,20,Fand screens in his home, and feared
OL,21,Fbeing followed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
