CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782676071
OL,3,CMan who damaged phone and media masts
OL,4,Cfound not criminally responsible
OL,6,FDuring that time, he also stopped
OL,7,Fanswering his phone and his family was
OL,8,Fso concerned that they travelled from
OL,9,FPoland to check on him.
OL,11,FBetween 2 and 4 July 2025, Szymanski
OL,12,Fdamaged six sites across the island -
OL,13,Fincluding the BBC Jersey radio
OL,14,Ftransmitter and satellite dish in
OL,15,FTrinity and five JT mobile masts in St
OL,16,FMary, St Ouen and St Lawrence.
OL,18,FThe total damage cost more than
OL,19,F#80,000 in repair bills and security
OL,20,Ffor telecoms firms JT and Arqiva, who
OL,21,Fmaintain the transmitter.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
