OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782676071
OL,3,CMan who damaged phone and media masts
OL,4,Cfound not criminally responsible
OL,6,FAfter hearing from two doctors
OL,7,Finvolved in Szymanski's care, Jurats
OL,8,Fdecided that he was not criminally
OL,9,Fresponsible and a treatment order was
OL,10,Fput in place to protect him and the
OL,11,Fcommunity.
OL,13,FCompensation claims from both of the
OL,14,Faffected companies were dismissed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/3
